#### Background Sync Service

```csharp
public class GmailSyncBackgroundService : BackgroundService
{
    // INTELLIGENT ADAPTIVE POLLING — frequency varies by transaction type:
    //
    // | Category           | Poll Interval | Gmail Query Filter                          |
    // |--------------------|---------------|---------------------------------------------|
    // | UPI / Daily Txns   | 10 minutes    | from:(alerts@*bank*) subject:(debited OR UPI)|
    // | Food (Swiggy/Zomato)| 10 minutes   | from:(*swiggy* OR *zomato*)                 |
    // | Subscriptions      | Daily (6 AM)  | from:(*netflix* OR *spotify* OR *aws*)      |
    // | EMI / Loans        | Monthly (1st) | subject:(EMI OR loan OR instalment)         |
    // | Salary             | Monthly (1st) | subject:(salary OR credit) amount > 10000   |
    // | Credit Card        | Daily (9 PM)  | from:(*card* OR *credit*)                   |
    //
    // The scheduler uses a SyncSchedule config per category.
    // All parsed transactions go to the REVIEW QUEUE (no auto-confirm).
    // Users can bulk-confirm items with confidence > 90% from the UI.
    //
    // For each user with HasGmailAccess == true:
    //   1. Check which category polls are due based on schedule
    //   2. Refresh Gmail access token if expired
    //   3. Query Gmail API with category-specific filters
    //   4. For each new email → run through parsing rules
    //   5. Store ParsedTransaction in staging (status = Pending)
    //   6. Notify frontend via SignalR that new transactions are available
}
```

